parameters:
\SE[36]I was casually feeding it, and before I knew it, it
had made itself at home... \SE[3]I call it Arter.

\SE[15]Oh... even beasts have human hearts, huh...?
\SE[16]Here, Arter...! Shake hands, one more time...
\SE[17]Good boy...!

\SE[2]That one doesn't listen to anyone's orders. \SE[37]At
most, there are slight signs during feeding.

\SE[16]Look, it's Arter...! Give me your hand, one more
time...\SE[17]Penis...! Ugh... Is it no good...!!

\SE[15]I can even handle 'Sable Noir'...! \!\SE[13]You
really are... \.'Such a fool'...!

\SE[2]Whether one can become a puppet is not a wise
criterion. \!\SE[37]...There is no reason to follow someone
more foolish than oneself.

\SE[17]No way!! It's obvious that being able to have a penis
is smarter...!! \SE[15]Dogs are different from cats, they
become attached easily...!!

\SE[3]The superior ones are those who are 'solitary'.
\!\SE[1]And the winners of 'selection' are the cats. It's
already a story that history has proven, right?

\SE[16]In terms of coexistence with humans, dogs are
superior...! Hunting dogs have repeatedly helped humans...!
\!\}\SE[15]Although Sable Noir is not good at hunting.

\SE[2]Hehe... It would be best to stop there. There is no
room for debate, as cats are superior.

\SE[17] (It's starting to feel like a pet bragging
competition...)

It sounds like a music box. This music can be heard from
here. Wow... it has a nice tone.

\SE[5] Chairman, I've been waiting... \!\SE[18]... We need
to go quickly.

\SE[39]The second floor is my bedroom. \SE[24]...I would
appreciate it if you could refrain from entering.

\SE[16]Oh... It has a very typical feeling... \SE[15]As
expected, this is how magicians are...

\SE[84]No, no... There are also many decent people... I'm
sure of it...

\SE[5]A 'magician'... seems like there isn't one around.
\!\SE[1]Hmm, should I try calling out?
I'll be free in a little while. Please wait there.
\SE[2]Good. It seems like you're not away.

\SE[2]I wonder why they live in a place like this? \SE[3]I
wonder if there's a reason for it?

\SE[76]Maybe they're a magician who wants to do
experiments or verification. \SE[3]They might be making sure
that there won't be any damage to the surroundings... or
something like that? \SE[76]...Or maybe they simply dislike
people.

I'm sorry. I kept you waiting. I've been having trouble
adjusting the new medicine....

\SE[92]I never expected to encounter you in this way...
\!\SE[91]...or rather, that you were still alive.

\SE[24]...I see. I understand the general idea. \SE[3]You
intend to use the power of Nagi... to save Lunaroa. That's
why you came here...

\SE[4]Will you hand it over obediently? \!\SE[3]Or will you
be mean and not hand it over to us, who were once your
enemies?

\SE[2]I am not such a small fry. \SE[1]I can give you as
much of this as you want. ...If you can accept one
condition.

\SE[37]It's nothing major... There is a cape ahead... Come
when you're ready. \SE[2]...I'll be waiting there.

\SE[4]Hmm... I met someone unexpected... \SE[3]It seems like
they're waiting ahead... What should we do?

\SE[17]We've come this far, we can't turn back now.
\SE[12]Just a little more... \SE[12]What's the matter...

\SE[90]Seems like it's not a big deal condition... but it
won't be easy, right? \SE[91]...Be prepared, at least.

The 'White Witch's Hideout' has been added to the
teleportation crystal!

It seems to be a gift from the villagers. Various feelings
of gratitude are written.

\SE[16]Huh... it's a bear.... \!\SE[15]It's a very good
bear...\. It has good taste....

After this, the unnecessary trial and error will be burned.
Everyone must stand on top of numerous 'failures'...
